\begin_inset Formula $\forall_{k\ge k_{0}}|f(x_{n_{k}})|=|f(x_{n_{k}})-f(x_{0})+f(x_{0})|\le|f(x_{n_{k}})-f(x_{0})|+|f(x_{0})|\overset{\text{(*)}}{<}1+|f(x_{0})|$
